<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Loan Plan - AgriFlow</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/agriflow.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar-agriflow') %>

        <!-- Result Container -->
        <section class="result-container">

            <!-- ===== SECTION 1: GREETING CARD ===== -->
            <div class="greeting-card fade-in">
                <h2>👋 नमस्ते, <%= farmer.name %>!</h2>
                <div class="farmer-details">
                    <p>🌾 फसल: <strong>
                            <%= farmer.crop %>
                        </strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 🏡 भूमि: <strong>
                            <%= farmer.land %> एकड़
                        </strong></p>
                    <p>💳 ऋण: <strong>₹<%= farmer.loan.toLocaleString() %></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ⏱️ अवधि: <strong>
                            <%= farmer.duration %>
                        </strong></p>
                    <p>📍 जिला: <strong>
                            <%= farmer.district %>
                        </strong></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== SECTION 2: RISK CARD (MOST IMPORTANT) ===== -->
            <div class="risk-card fade-in risk-<%= farmer.riskLevel.toLowerCase() %>">
                <div class="risk-emoji">
                    <%= farmer.riskEmoji %>
                </div>
                <h3 class="risk-title">आपका जोखिम स्तर / Your Risk Level: <strong>
                        <%= farmer.riskLevel %>
                    </strong></h3>

                <div class="risk-score">
                    <%= farmer.riskScore %> / 100
                </div>

                <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div class="progress-fill" style="width: <%= farmer.riskScore %>%;"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="risk-explanation">
                    <% if (farmer.riskLevel==='Low' ) { %>
                        <p>✅ बहुत अच्छा! आप समय पर ऋण चुकाने की क्षमता रखते हैं। / Great! You are likely to repay your
                            loan on time.</p>
                        <% } else if (farmer.riskLevel==='Medium' ) { %>
                            <p>⚡ सावधान रहें! ऋण लेने से पहले अपने खर्च कम करने की कोशिश करें। / Be careful. Try to
                                reduce expenses before taking loan.</p>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <p>⚠️ उच्च जोखिम! कृपया किसी वित्तीय सलाहकार से बात करें। / High risk. Please talk to a
                                    financial advisor first.</p>
                                <% } %>
                </div>

                <hr style="margin: 1.5rem 0; border: none; border-top: 2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

                <!-- Risk Breakdown - FIXED READABILITY -->
                <div
                    style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1rem; border: 2px solid #ddd;">
                    <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;">📊 जोखिम की
                        गणना / Risk Calculation Breakdown:</h4>

                    <div
                        style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; color: #333; font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        <!-- Factor 1: EMI Burden (Most Important) -->
                        <div
                            style="background: #fff9f0; padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; border-left: 5px solid #ff6b6b; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0; font-weight: 600; color: #d32f2f; font-size: 1rem;">
                                <strong>⚠️ EMI का बोझ / EMI Burden</strong>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>बदतर महीना / Worst:</strong> <span
                                    style="color: #d32f2f; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                                    <%= farmer.emiPercentageWorst %>%
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>औसत / Average:</strong> <span style="color: #f57c00; font-weight: 600;">
                                    <%= farmer.emiPercentageAvg %>%
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; font-style: italic;">
                                <% if (farmer.emiPercentageWorst> 50) { %>
                                    ❌ बहुत ज्यादा जोखिम / Very High Risk
                                    <% } else if (farmer.emiPercentageWorst> 40) { %>
                                        ❌ ज्यादा जोखिम / High Risk
                                        <% } else if (farmer.emiPercentageWorst> 30) { %>
                                            ⚡ माध्यम जोखिम / Medium Risk
                                            <% } else if (farmer.emiPercentageWorst> 20) { %>
                                                ✅ कम-माध्यम जोखिम / Low-Medium Risk
                                                <% } else { %>
                                                    ✅ कम जोखिम / Low Risk
                                                    <% } %>
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Factor 2: Loan-to-Land Ratio -->
                        <div
                            style="background: #f0f9ff; padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; border-left: 5px solid #4ecdc4; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0; font-weight: 600; color: #00838f; font-size: 1rem;">
                                <strong>🏡 ऋण-भूमि अनुपात / Loan-to-Land</strong>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>प्रति एकड़ / Per Acre:</strong> <span
                                    style="color: #00838f; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                                    ₹<%= (farmer.loan / farmer.land).toLocaleString() %>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>मासिक EMI / Monthly:</strong> <span style="color: #2e7d32; font-weight: 600;">
                                    ₹<%= farmer.monthlyEMI.toLocaleString() %>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666;">
                                ✅ ₹50,000/एकड़ तक सुरक्षित / Up to ₹50K/acre safe
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Income Details -->
                        <div
                            style="background: #f0fdf4; padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; border-left: 5px solid #95e1d3; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0; font-weight: 600; color: #2e7d32; font-size: 1rem;">
                                <strong>💰 आय विवरण / Income</strong>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>औसत आय / Average:</strong> <span
                                    style="color: #2e7d32; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                                    ₹<%= farmer.averageMonthlyIncome.toLocaleString() %>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>न्यूनतम आय / Minimum:</strong> <span style="color: #f57c00; font-weight: 600;">
                                    ₹<%= farmer.lowestIncome.toLocaleString() %>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666;">
                                मौसमी भिन्नता के साथ / With seasonal variation
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Risk Level Guide -->
                        <div
                            style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; border-left: 5px solid #667eea; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0; font-weight: 600; color: #667eea; font-size: 1rem;">
                                <strong>📈 जोखिम स्तर / Risk Levels</strong>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>✅ कम / Low:</strong> <span style="color: #2e7d32;">0-40</span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>⚡ माध्यम / Medium:</strong> <span style="color: #f57c00;">40-65</span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555;">
                                <strong>⚠️ उच्च / High:</strong> <span style="color: #d32f2f;">65-100</span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; font-weight: 600;">
                                आपका स्कोर / Your Score: <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #667eea;">
                                    <%= farmer.riskScore %>
                                </span>/100
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== SECTION 3.5: EMI EXPLANATION ===== -->
            <div class="info-card fade-in"
                style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; grid-column: 1/4; padding: 2rem;">
                <h3 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📊 कैसे EMI की गणना की गई है? / How is EMI Calculated?
                </h3>
                <div style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <p><strong>सूत्र / Formula:</strong></p>
                    <p
                        style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin: 1rem 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffeb3b;">
                        <strong>EMI = कुल ऋण ÷ महीनों की संख्या</strong><br>
                        EMI = ₹<%= farmer.loan.toLocaleString() %> ÷ <%= farmer.durationMonths %> महीने = <strong
                                    style="font-size: 1.3rem; color: #ffeb3b;">₹<%= farmer.monthlyEMI.toLocaleString()
                                        %>/महीना</strong>
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>मुख्य जानकारी / Key Information:</strong></p>
                    <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                        <li>कुल राशि (मूल + ब्याज) / Total (Principal + Interest): <strong style="color: #c8e6c9;">₹<%=
                                    farmer.totalAmount.toLocaleString() %></strong></li>
                        <li>अनुमानित ब्याज (10% p.a.) / Estimated Interest: <strong style="color: #c8e6c9;">₹<%=
                                    farmer.totalInterest.toLocaleString() %></strong></li>
                        <li>अवधि लाभ / Duration Benefit: <strong style="color: #90ee90;">
                                <%= farmer.durationDiscount %>% छूट = कम जोखिम
                            </strong></li>
                        <li>प्रतिशत = (EMI ÷ आपकी आय) × 100 / Percentage = (EMI ÷ Your Income) × 100</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div
                        style="background: rgba(144, 238, 144, 0.1); padding: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; border-left: 4px solid #90ee90;">
                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #c8e6c9;">
                            💡 <strong>टिप्पणी:</strong> लंबी अवधि के ऋण सुरक्षित हैं - 36 महीने तक 40% जोखिम में कमी
                            पाएँ!
                            <br>
                            <strong>Note:</strong> Longer loans are safer - Get up to 40% risk reduction for 36 months!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== SECTION 3.6: INFO CARDS REPEATED (IF NEEDED) ===== -->

            <!-- ===== SECTION 4: INCOME CHART ===== -->
            <div class="chart-container fade-in" data-income-months="<%= JSON.stringify(farmer.monthlyIncome) %>">
                <h3 class="chart-title">💰 आपकी अपेक्षित आय - महीना दर महीना / Your Expected Income - Month by Month
                </h3>
                <canvas id="incomeChart"></canvas>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== SECTION 5: EMI TABLE ===== -->
            <div class="emi-table-container fade-in">
                <h3 class="emi-table-title">📅 आपकी EMI योजना / Your EMI Plan
                    <span style="color: #667eea; font-size: 0.9rem;">(<%= farmer.durationMonths %> Months - <%=
                                farmer.durationDiscount %>% Safe)</span>
                </h3>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    ✅ <%= farmer.durationMonths %>-महीने की अवधि में कम जोखिम / <%= farmer.durationMonths %>-month loan
                            reduces risk by <%= farmer.durationDiscount %>%<br>
                                ✅ यह तालिका आपके <%= farmer.durationMonths %> महीने की ऋण अवधि के लिए EMI दिखाती है।
                </p>
                <table class="emi-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>महीना / Month</th>
                            <th>आपकी आय / Income</th>
                            <th>EMI दर / EMI to Pay</th>
                            <th>प्रतिशत / %</th>
                            <th>स्थिति / Status</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% farmer.emiPlan.forEach(plan=> { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>
                                        <%= plan.monthEng %> (Month <%= plan.monthNumber %>)
                                    </strong></td>
                                <td>₹<%= plan.income.toLocaleString() %>
                                </td>
                                <td>₹<%= plan.emi.toLocaleString() %>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <%= plan.percent %>%
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <% if (plan.status==='safe' ) { %>
                                        <span class="emi-status-safe">✅ सुरक्षित / Safe</span>
                                        <% } else if (plan.status==='medium' ) { %>
                                            <span class="emi-status-medium">⚡ सावधान / Caution</span>
                                            <% } else { %>
                                                <span class="emi-status-high">⚠️ उच्च / High</span>
                                                <% } %>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <% }); %>
                                <% if (farmer.emiPlan.totalMonths && farmer.emiPlan.totalMonths> 12) { %>
                                    <tr style="background: #f0f0f0; font-weight: bold;">
                                        <td colspan="5" style="text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem;">
                                            ... और <%= farmer.emiPlan.remainingMonths %> महीने अधिक / + <%=
                                                    farmer.emiPlan.remainingMonths %> more months ...
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <% } %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <div
                    style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #1b5e20;"><strong>💡 सुरक्षा के नियम /
                            Safety Rules:</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2e7d32;">✅ EMI आपकी आय का <strong>30% से
                            कम</strong> होना चाहिए। / EMI should be <strong>less than 30%</strong> of your income.</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #d32f2f;">❌ यदि EMI <strong>40% से
                            अधिक</strong> है, तो यह जोखिम भरा है। / If EMI is <strong>more than 40%</strong>, it's
                        risky.</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #f57c00;">⚡ <strong>30-40%</strong> के बीच
                        सावधानी बरतें। / Between 30-40%, proceed with caution.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== SECTION 6: TIPS FOR FARMER ===== -->
            <div class="tips-section fade-in">
                <h2 class="tips-title">💡 आपके लिए सुझाव / Our Suggestions for You</h2>
                <div class="tips-grid">
                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-icon">🌧️</div>
                        <div class="tip-text">बारिश के मौसम से पहले फसल बीमा कराएँ / Get crop insurance before rainy
                            season</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-icon">📦</div>
                        <div class="tip-text">गेहूं को मार्च में बेचें, ज्यादा कीमत मिलेगी / Sell wheat in March for
                            better price</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-icon">💧</div>
                        <div class="tip-text">ड्रिप सिंचाई से पानी बचाएँ 40% तक / Drip irrigation saves 40% water</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-icon">💪</div>
                        <div class="tip-text">समय पर EMI दें, अपना स्कोर सुधारें / Pay EMI on time to improve credit
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-icon">🤝</div>
                        <div class="tip-text">किसान समूह से जुड़ें, बेहतर मूल्य पाएँ / Join farmer group for better
                            prices</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-icon">📞</div>
                        <div class="tip-text">किसी भी समस्या पर अपने बैंक से बात करें / Talk to bank for any issues
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== SECTION 7: ACTION BUTTONS ===== -->
            <div style="margin: 3rem 0; text-align: center;">
                <div class="action-buttons">
                    <a href="/agriflow/apply" class="btn-primary">🔁 फिर से जांचें / Check Again</a>
                    <a href="tel:+919876543210" class="btn-secondary">📞 सलाहकार से बात करें / Talk to Advisor</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Final Message -->
            <div
                style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #c8e6c9 100%); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1.5rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0;">
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #1b5e20; font-weight: 600;">
                    ✅ आपकी ऋण योजना तैयार है! / Your loan plan is ready!
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #333; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                    अब अपने नजदीकी बैंक में जाएँ और आवेदन करें / Visit your nearest bank and apply now
                </p>
            </div>

        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <%- include('partials/footer-agriflow') %>

            <script src="/js/agriflow.js"></script>
            <script>
                // Initialize chart when page loads
                document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
                    const incomeDataElement = document.querySelector('[data-income-months]');
                    if (incomeDataElement) {
                        const incomeData = JSON.parse(incomeDataElement.dataset.incomeMonths);
                        initIncomeChart(incomeData);
                    }

                    // Animate progress bar
                    const progressFill = document.querySelector('.progress-fill');
                    if (progressFill) {
                        const targetWidth = parseFloat(progressFill.style.width);
                        progressFill.style.width = '0%';
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            progressFill.style.transition = 'width 1s ease-out';
                            progressFill.style.width = targetWidth + '%';
                        }, 100);
                    }
                });
            </script>
</body>

</html>